name: Enter Leave Period Name in Search Box for Leave Tab

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Leave Period Name in Search Box for Leave Tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, leavePeriod=25-Sep-2022 to 26-Sep-2022})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When User Enters "25-Sep-2022 to 26-Sep-2022" period in search box for "Leave" tab
Then Verify "25-Sep-2022 to 26-Sep-2022" Period is filtered for "Leave" tab
